This directory contains a modified copy of the Memos frontend
(https://github.com/usememos/memos), licensed under the MIT License.

Modifications:
- Configured Vite base path for serving under the /memos/ URL subpath
- ConnectRPC and REST API URLs prefixed with /memos/
- React Router basename set to /memos
- File/attachment URLs prefixed with /memos/
- Auth redirect paths prefixed with /memos/
- SSE endpoint URL prefixed with /memos/
- Suppressed i18next/Locize console advertisement

